platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Zillow can help you find the home of your dreams—one that contains all of your must-haves, is a reasonable distance from work, and falls (kind of) within your budget. The app offers resources for every step in the process, from attending open houses to picking an agent to understanding the intricacies of the mortgage market.

Offering resources for every step in the process, from attending open houses to picking an agent and understanding the intricacies of the mortgage market, this app will help you find the home of your dreams.

這款房地產 App 提供你找房子過程中的各種資源，從參觀開放房屋到選擇房地產經紀人，從瞭解房貸市場的複雜性到完成交易，一路幫你找到理想的家。
